This is a Drupal module intended to authenticate users against a Leaguerunner
database accessible by the drupal database user on the same MySQL server.

CONVERTING FROM 4.x
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
When converting from a 4.x drupal, it will be necessary to modify the
'authname' column of 'authmap', and the 'init' column of 'users', so that the
entries are suffixed with '@leaguerunner' instead of '@ocua'.

